Make the Script Executable:  chmod +x /path/to/debezium_streaming.sh

Create a systemd Service File:  sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/debezium-streaming.service

Add the Following Content: 
[Unit]
Description=Debezium Streaming Service
After=network.target

[Service]
ExecStart=/path/to/debezium_streaming.sh
Restart=always
User=your_username
WorkingDirectory=/path/to/your/django/project # Optional: Set the working directory for your Django project

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target

#Replace /path/to/debezium_streaming.sh with the actual path to your script.
#Replace your_username with your system username.
#Optionally, set the WorkingDirectory to the directory of your Django project.

Reload systemd: sudo systemctl daemon-reload
Start the Service: sudo systemctl start debezium-streaming
Enable the Service to Start on Boot: sudo systemctl enable debezium-streaming
Check the Status of the Service: sudo systemctl status debezium-streaming
View Logs: sudo journalctl -u debezium-streaming -f
